'''波司登长江大桥'''，又名“'''合江长江一桥'''”，是中国[[四川省|四川省]][[泸州市|泸州市]][[合江县|合江县]]的一座长江大桥，是{{China Expwy Name|G93}}的过江通道之一，主跨{{convert|530|m|ft|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.best-news.us/news-4581737-The-world-39s-largest-steel-arch-bridge-span-Lu-Chongqing-high-speed-connectivity.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228113807/http://www.best-news.us/news-4581737-The-world-39s-largest-steel-arch-bridge-span-Lu-Chongqing-high-speed-connectivity.html |archivedate=2014-02-28 }}</ref>，超过了[[巫山长江大桥|巫山长江大桥]]，成为[[世界拱桥列表|世界上跨径最大的]]钢管混凝土[[拱桥|拱桥]]。<ref>http://www.arch-bridges.com/paper2010/pdf/13-Scheme%20design%20of%20a%20530m%20CFST%20arch%20bridge--the%20First%20Yangtze%20River%20Bridge%20in%20Hejiang,%20Sichuan,%20China.pdf {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301033521/http://www.arch-bridges.com/paper2010/pdf/13-Scheme%20design%20of%20a%20530m%20CFST%20arch%20bridge--the%20First%20Yangtze%20River%20Bridge%20in%20Hejiang%2C%20Sichuan%2C%20China.pdf |date=2014-03-01 }}</ref>

